[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering whether to use AssertJ's assertion for checking the existence of a Path, which is supported in version 3.22. There’s a potential issue related to clearing library paths, as it might affect class loading when running tests in the same JVM. I realize the Native Image won’t allow System.load with JNI due to the included config. It seems unnecessary to modify metadata since the upstream jline jar already includes this. One test can cover all scenarios, which simplifies things!
[thinking] 
